			<div class="comment-body"><div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_1168208_comm_506"></div><p>I think you hit on a point that many fail to realize is one of Bitcoin&#8217;s greatest strengths: Programmatic Manipulation.  Never has money been accessible to code in such a raw way.  As a consequence Bitcoin is far more chameleon than its critics realize.  Many problems are hardly problems at all.  They just represent future optimizations that have yet to come.</p>
</div>

